title: Li Keqiang Sends Congratulatory Message to Lee Hsien Loong for His Re-election as Prime Minister ...
text: ( Source : Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the People's Republic of China ) On October 1, 2015 , Premier Li Keqiang sent a congratulatory message to Lee Hsien Loong for his re-election as Prime Minister of the Republic of Singapore . Li Keqiang
